#: apps_libreoffice.xml:263
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Contains loading and saving specific options. For example, you can choose "
"whether to always create a backup copy and which file format &libo; should "
"use by default."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: apps_libreoffice.xml:272
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To learn more about configuring &libo;, see <xref linkend=\"sec.oo.oview."
"global\"/>."
