"personal certificate, similar to an HTTPS certificate. You can either create "
"a self-signed certificate or choose to obtain one from a Certificate "
"Authority."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: apps_libreoffice.xml:642
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When applying a digital signature to a document, a kind of checksum is "
"created from the document's content and your personal key. The checksum is "
"stored together with the document."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: apps_libreoffice.xml:648
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When another person opens the document, the checksum will be generated "
"again. The new checksum is then compared to the original checksum. If both "
"are equal, the application will signal that the document has not been "
"changed in the meantime."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
